mal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無 係一時時先有聲 多數企好耐之後就會有聲"},{"pid":"106541368593e146d6dbeef7c41393408696767f","tid":144193,"uid":84265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:52:38.000Z","msg":"我都係咁，已經過左十幾年<br />\n照過x光都話無事，但隻腳轉唔到好大角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82976635dce95c7cc437dc0d3cac1cc322cecc0a","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁，已經過左十幾年<br />\n照過x光都話無事，但隻腳轉唔到好大角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉唔到可能係d臼位硬咗<br />\n不過你都十幾年應該無得救"},{"pid":"01395c6c7191b6d4db28f38e6b6645d28b5acb62","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁，已經過左十幾年<br />\n照過x光都話無事，但隻腳轉唔到好大角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁做運動有無問題？<br />\n有無痛個d"},{"pid":"61343c4ad7462710a92eeccf56ba816fe123a5c0","tid":144193,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你舊骨移左位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪一定要睇西醫？<br />\n定係唔洗理？</blockquote><br />\n識搞可以自己擰返正，踢波拗過三次依家無啪啪聲無漲大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c66dd0bfc903ba9edb0e8636affccb62fb6647d","tid":144193,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"有無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係企得耐會有啪啪聲"},{"pid":"c18a5a8466c1b980b73a4a29cc41e4e0573afd06","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-0