ssets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇左幾次之後做埋物理治療同我講唔洗再睇 但到e家隻腳舊骨大左,落雨同打波都有時會痛 係咪成世都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已經成8個月"},{"pid":"8fba6159fc0201ecb577aa67fda2291c5f4c187d","tid":144193,"uid":9217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上年拗左腳 第2日已經去睇跌打仲照埋X光 之後睇左十次好返小小無再去睇 但之後隻腳仲係行得好唔舒服同打波會痛 之後去睇骨科同我講我舊骨裂左小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇左幾次之後做埋物理治療同我講唔洗再睇 但到e家隻腳舊骨大左,落雨同打波都有時會痛 係咪成世都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已經成8個月</blockquote><br />\n風濕<br />\n玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315150685f2eb538401b197c87c387b85436ed74","tid":144193,"uid":19018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我上年拗左腳 第2日已經去睇跌打仲照埋X光 之後睇左十次好返小小無再去睇 但之後隻腳仲係行得好唔舒服同打波會痛 之後去睇骨科同我講我舊骨裂左小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇左幾次之後做埋物理治療同我講唔洗再睇 但到e家隻腳舊骨大左,落雨同打波都有時會痛 係咪成世都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已經成8個月</blockquote><br />\n風濕<br />\n玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要隻腳仲睇到有腫 利申：得21歲仔"},{"pid":"84d831a5eeddb9974685bdfb017c17e1453957a4","tid":144193,"uid":19018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb6efb8d1d5b703fc63fe696f395109eccb4713","tid":144193,"uid":54174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"拗到atfl同ptfl都撕裂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2194f13929d0ccdc3fdd16bf6ac76de9bf2df7","tid":144193,"uid":16953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"拗柴去睇跌打定去睇骨科好<br />\n事關我已經係慣性拗柴<br />\n行平路都可以拗一拗<br />\n前日拗咗獲勁嘅<br />\n即刻行唔到路<br />\n我番屋企立即搵冰敷佢<br />\n到第二日先係可以扶住把遮忍住痛行下咁<br />\n但係仲未消腫<br />\n好驚軟骨個啲有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我每次拗柴拗到要抖1個月嘅都係右腳<br />\n離上次整親大抖1個月後 因為睇跌打好貴 <br />\n我見冇咩事 仲有少少痛就唔睇 <br />\n點知宜家又整獲大嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊睇跌打好定睇骨科好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe197a531f3b944d5c4653d5ca9caeea31c57f5b","tid":144193,"uid":13594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:09:25.000Z","msg":"隻腳摸落去舊骨大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251dc201f918415a39d20865e4158ac413c871b7","tid":144193,"uid":62717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:15:12.000Z","msg":"你個野壞左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b729cc7221364850f7f246b9d4645025b76b279","tid":144193,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:15:44.000Z","msg":"之前係咁唔消腫去睇物理治療<br />\n照過超聲波話裂左兩條韌帶<br />\n無得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021892885f283580dfa749600cb46bcbc623ad0d","tid":144193,"uid":34772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:42:54.000Z","msg":"做過排physio又好左少少 有排真係完全冇啪啪聲 停左冇做 點知而家又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0471ee5abced91ab604bc98fe1d1d54122e612de","tid":144193,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/024451_d57bdac89ae915e7a3dad6e951ec8695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F024451_d57bdac89ae915e7a3dad6e951ec8695.jpg&h=1d442c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等我好翻答你！"},{"pid":"32eb9b8c77aaf264cf5d64e2add0e1ea0591caad","tid":144193,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:48:48.000Z","msg":"大左少少 <br />\n即使好番5/6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125d4124c444818c4369ced52fc56d6080e5a70d","tid":144193,"uid":1266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:49:02.000Z","msg":"屌我都係 係咪冇得較<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c81b635d4e790e99b17ada0d6bbc3d8b7f1350","tid":144193,"uid":32882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:52:48.000Z","msg":"手同腳都拗左十幾年<br />\n四個位一轉都會啪啪聲<br />\n四個位都會有舊骨突出黎"},{"pid":"711c7d9cbb0821ad2c752852f548df38fe3d4962","tid":144193,"uid":10342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:07:53.000Z","msg":"認真答 組織增生"},{"pid":"e0311b9977ca5e28299f883cbae42a662dcf51d9","tid":144193,"uid":30341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:28:08.000Z","msg":"我唔記得有冇拗過，但腳眼下面生多舊骨  依家大過腳眼，照x光醫生又話照唔到有舊骨"},{"pid":"a435c54f6d6f013e014e81aafef1c29c08d047b0","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大左少少 <br />\n即使好番5/6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d214698f1e3df68dfb9916120abab570b77ed3b","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌我都係 係咪冇得較<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係想知踢唔踢得返波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e17b26592a1e8e2778a24723a0b4b10d2e163b","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答 組織增生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪唔洗理?"},{"pid":"999806f19a832eceb4a7fb55a760ace67107eedb","tid":144193,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身體知你嗰度傷咗，軟組織增生，保護返隻腳"},{"pid":"6f6f3edc97ba3d31db8d95f3f79ce7d8ae7bd571","tid":144193,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>+1 轉個關節有聲出<br />\n<br />\n利申:兩隻腳拗曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n！！有同病相憐者！！到底係咩事，係咪永遠都係咁架喇？<br />\n好在我得右腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13791dfc80929d1a4fc9de4c78148a803b2c04e","tid":144193,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:44:51.000Z","msg":"成九年<br />\n隻腳成日都好似有野銀住"},{"pid":"aeeb6ad0afdeb47c653bd8f92516e61a04621e04","tid":144193,"uid":38938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:47:34.000Z","msg":"我係隻左腳踝有個位腫痛左好耐<br />\n之後個痛到上膝蓋下位舊肌肉<br />\n<br />\n應該點醫"},{"pid":"4186e4adcd593b3c3afe83f094ce697315e8fca4","tid":144193,"uid":20528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:56:38.000Z","msg":"試過拗柴跟住個跌打佬話我舊骨移左位 之後幫我推返入去 又好似真係細舊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb956e33ab0c579276645daa9a5fcd95993d4934","tid":144193,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過拗柴跟住個跌打佬話我舊骨移左位 之後幫我推返入去 又好似真係細舊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個拗親 跌打幫我扭幾扭包好隻腳就完事 但一個月之後仲腫 好彩睇骨醫幫我正骨之後先消"},{"pid":"058e01b6f9a392be76449e38107af7046d6d89f6","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過拗柴跟住個跌打佬話我舊骨移左位 之後幫我推返入去 又好似真係細舊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45079ca8cb09353190d59bb6aa99ad15d951fb9a","tid":144193,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"通常做運動容易咬柴本身都係天生肌肉有唔平衡，照X光睇唔到問題，嚮骨科角度已經冇野可以做，但其實要做多啲糾正運動，過弱肌肉練返緊，過勞肌肉拉返鬆，平時多著boot避免咬柴"},{"pid":"20f0b61e179185f3b315d1a935c8f4cfe9904c0b","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常做運動容易咬柴本身都係天生肌肉有唔平衡，照X光睇唔到問題，嚮骨科角度已經冇野可以做，但其實要做多啲糾正運動，過弱肌肉練返緊，過勞肌肉拉返鬆，平時多著boot避免咬柴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係比人推跌再擲到咬柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e767572f93cab3ee86b8e434fd9b8fc7513ed997","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d7ca0896da5ccf61261ced9a95e304af1a7504","tid":144193,"uid":74335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:04:17.000Z","msg":"我拗左三次右腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 右腳同左腳一比，隻右腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e661362840b7dd31db9c24dab1b6ace6a1a8012e","tid":144193,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我拗左三次右腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 右腳同左腳一比，隻右腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照張相黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打波整親?"},{"pid":"f14289266d9827905db254db2aac1067c24d8731","tid":144193,"uid":39536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過拗柴跟住個跌打佬話我舊骨移左位 之後幫我推返入去 又好似真係細舊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個拗親 跌打幫我扭幾扭包好隻腳就完事 但一個月之後仲腫 好彩睇骨醫幫我正骨之後先消</blockquote><br />\n跌打痴線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813f51e33637dd56a80f40cb67b37718fbad3edd","tid":144193,"uid":41858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5637AV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5637AV.jpg&h=a1e4e4c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我半個月前整襯，睇極都無好轉，消唔到腫。早幾日先睇左個幾好嘅跌打師傅，但都係無用。今個禮拜仲要打比賽，你話死唔死"},{"pid":"7ff45c95df807ba8043b1145cb1ff257bc4037fc","tid":144193,"uid":29845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5637AV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5637AV.jpg&h=a1e4e4c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我半個月前整襯，睇極都無好轉，消唔到腫。早幾日先睇左個幾好嘅跌打師傅，但都係無用。今個禮拜仲要打比賽，你話死唔死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真 唔好去打比賽(真係唔miss得無計) 再傷你會好後悔 <br />\n我幾年前試過踢波拗親繼續踢 變到好腫 睇濕鳩跌打又斷唔好尾 個位變左舊患"},{"pid":"1cf18be005fbb40e43bb5cd9cbdcf9b386219829","tid":144193,"uid":19916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor